    dc:description "Figure 10. Phintella platnicki Sudhin, Sen & Caleb, 2023, from Kerala. A. Male, dorsal view; B. Female, dorsal view; C. Male, frontal view; D. Female, frontal view. Scale bars: 1 mm (A-D)." ;
