    dc:description "Figure 11. Phintella platnicki Sudhin, Sen & Caleb, 2023, from Karnataka (A-D) and from Kerala (E-H). A, E. Left male palp, ventral view; B, F. Same, retrolateral view; C, G. Female epigyne, ventral view; D, H. Vulva, dorsal view. Scale bars: 0.2 mm (A-F); 0.1 mm (G-H)." ;
